      <title>Tech Tuesday Training: Better Notes Start with OneNote</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/52488156022240/huge/2d8cca0cf860768829e5b99179faa9f41cb3879b.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Tue, 12 May 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>Better Notes Start with OneNote</p>

